      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve<strong> </strong>all the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>butter beans</strong></p>",
